{"tid":1972553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【屌你老母】員佐級協會就禁止公眾查閱選民登記冊一案上訴 獲批臨時禁制令","createTime":"2020-04-14T14:56:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-14T16:37:33.000Z","uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"21bb96b42dc225ffb9d694af026211f51792a128","tid":1972553,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3375666959208003/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F3375666959208003%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=toob0nj6ijAdanGp0CPeWb7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=74917526\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3375666959208003/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n記協表示，得悉警察員佐級協會決定就禁止公眾查閱選民登記冊一案上訴，並申請緊急臨時禁制令禁止公眾查閱選民登記冊。法院暫批准臨時禁制令，下星期一再作決定，另定於5月5日處理開庭上訴申請。記協對事件表示極度關注，並會密切留意發展，如有需要將再循司法途徑介入。<br />\n<br />\n高等法院上星期三否決警察員佐級協會就禁止公眾查閱選民登記冊之司法覆核申請，選舉事務處隨後亦公布將於明天恢復提供2019年地方選區正式選民登記冊、功能界別正式選民登記冊及界別分組正式投票人登記冊供公眾查閱。"},{"pid":"61fd42bb2282afc2fee754997015cd89821e951a","tid":1972553,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PagWGtQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPagWGtQ.jpg&h=e43a4ce6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2181bc57e7a08ff0da66efd29a8ea40c656e81e","tid":1972553,"uid":245065,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:57:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d562b031def0e68b2ca7ab39c7aa16543d04665","tid":1972553,"uid":57088,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"21bb96b42dc225ffb9d694af026211f51792a128","tid":1972553,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-14T14:56:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3375666959208003/?type=3&amp;theater\" da